3 Months Ago Also recall that SaharaReporters had on Monday exclusively reported that Kyari was gravely ill and had in fact contracted Coronavirus. The next day on Tuesday, SaharaReporters also broke the story of three of Kyari's staff testing positive for the deadly virus. 



